properties.name: mapDescription
properties.value:
Suitable for up to 200 users.

Yes you can organize your event in this space station.
But beware, I see you coming... here there is no question of reporting corpses or voting to expel an impostor and the only emergency meeting will be to find out who has an extra swimsuit!
